text:
EFL JESUS WEPT Manchester City star Gabriel Jesus was forced to withdraw from the match against Bournemouth after just 14 minutes as he left the field in tears 
Bournemouth suffered their own first half injury woes as Jack Wilshere on-loan from Arsenal had to come off after a tackle on David Silva by MARK IRWIN and jake lambourne 13th February 2017, 8:39 pm
